  The Appalachian Party BarnThe perfect venue for your special event. With its desirable amenities, including chandeliers, heat and air conditioning, restrooms, and lodging, it can accommodate groups of up to 200 guests or more. You can even add a tent to the space for additional seating. The barn features a country chic image, with white drapes and lights that brighten the space in the winter and provide a scenic backdrop in the summer when the doors are open. And with ample parking, your guests will have no trouble accessing the site. Connected to the Appalachian Party Barn is the Brick Patio. Our spacious patio measures 40 x 60 feet, making it the perfect location for your next event. When fully covered by a tint, the patio can accommodate up to 300 guests, providing plenty of room for mingling, dancing, and celebrating.

